{"tid":432581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［秋後算賬］伊拉克法院下令逮捕庫德族獨立公投攪手","createTime":"2017-10-11T15:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T15:54:06.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4d38cf923dd8e87cd8b38b02657d38f3b19d071e","tid":432581,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕伊拉克政府對庫德族獨立公投有最新行動，伊拉克法院週三（11日）下令，逮捕獨立公投的3名組織者。<br />\n《法新社》報導，伊拉克最高司法委員會發言人Abdel Sattar Bayraqdar表示，巴格達東部的法院是依照總理阿巴迪（Haider al-Abadi）率領的國家安全委員會的要求發出命令。<br />\n法院對獨立選舉和公投委員會主席沙勒（Hendren Saleh）和另外2名成員奧瑪（Yari Hajji Omar）、赫梅茲（Wahida Yofo Hermez）發出逮捕令。<br />\n法院裁定，上述3人「組織公投違反伊拉克最高法院的裁決」，法院已指此舉違法憲法規定，並下令撤銷。<br />\n伊拉克政府已通過切斷庫德族自治區和其他地區的國際航線，阻止庫德族與外界聯繫。週一，當局已對庫德族官員展開法律攻勢。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2219912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2219912&d=yPJiFznuub29aD1mpa7tk%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=57229928\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2219912&h=f6d9532e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2219912</a><br />\n果然要殺雞儆猴"},{"pid":"f4392378aa5f01f3560601142b0151bf3af18f79","tid":432581,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"伊拉克有本事就派兵入庫爾德地區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b202ccee7c877a43840102b5cc45344dd36b9186","tid":432581,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"美國仲要利用庫德族打ISIS"}]}